OL,4,CSmall shops face #1.7bn debt mountain,
OL,5,Csays report
OL,6, The UK's small shopkeepers are
OL,7, struggling under a #1.7bn mountain of
OL,8, debt, a former retail chief has warned.
OL,10,FIndependent High Street businesses now
OL,11,Fowe four times as much as they did a
OL,12,Fyear ago, said Bill Grimsey, ex-boss of
OL,13,FWickes, Iceland and Focus DIY.
OL,15,FThe warning comes in his latest report
OL,16,Finto the future of town centres and
OL,17,FHigh Streets.
OL,19,FUnless the government steps in, the UK
OL,20,Fcould face a "tsunami" of shop closures
OL,21,Fthis autumn, he said.
